FBIS4-4925 "dreas066_c_94046" FBIS-EAS-94-066 Daily Report 3 Apr 1994 North Korea Art Troupes Arrive for Friendship Art Festival Art Troupes Arrive for Friendship Art Festival SK0304085194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0807 GMT 3 Apr 94 SK0304085194 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 3 (KCNA) -- An art troupe of the International Federation of Koreans for Reunification and a Kazakh art troupe arrived here Saturday to participate in the 12th April spring friendship art festival. They were met at the airport by Choe Yong-ku, vice-minister of Culture and Art, and other officials concerned. Earlier, an art troupe of Koreans in China arrived here by train.
